values: One of the most amazing nights of my life. Ever. Wow. I'm gonna go to sleep now and wakeup in 3 hours...But it's gonna be the best 3 hours of sleep ever. And tomorrow will be wonderful.

Truth Meme

1. Every person who wishes, may ask me one question in the form of a comment attached to this post.

2. Out of respect for you, I will answer the question completely honestly. No matter how painful the answer may be.

3. If you ask me a question, you must post this meme in your journal so that the favor may be reciprocated. Otherwise, I will either give a lie in answer to your question or not answer at all.

So I just got accepted to Charlotte. I can't explain how happy I am. I could just type in all capital letters and put lots of exclamation points and type a bunch of crazy shit. But I won't. I'm just going to say that I feel so...Relieved. I finally have my life on course. I'm actually going to do something this time. It's almost set in stone.
I'm an asshole and I want the world to know it.

It's funny how fast things can change when you really want them to and you take that first step. 

New job for the win!

I've come to the conclusion that the world is a terrible, sad, pathetic, worthless place to be. Unfortunately we're stuck here. But we're the reason the world is what it is. It's not the world after all, it's the people of the world. We all deserve to burn in hell.

Well I almost died of some evil virus. I've never been so sick. A whole week of lying in bed and sweating and not being able to sleep and aching and dying over and over. But I'm alive again. It's all good now. I'm gonna start school in January or so...Gonna go to Florida in October or November for the wedding...Gonna have fun. Gonna get a 02 or 03 Grand Prix in December or so...Good stuff! Went back to work today...Blah. After losing 10 pounds from being sick I gotta get back in the routine and working out. Gonna be buff!

Boring day...Woke up at 12ish...It was all rainy outside so I didn't feel like going to the gym. I went to work at 4 and had a normal day there...Turned in my 2 weeks today. Came home, ate, played computer a bit...Natalie called me around 11. Talked to her for almost an hour about absolutely nothing...Don't know what to do with that girl...Ah well

Parents leave for Connecticut tomorrow and get back Saturday. Gotta get up at 7 tomorrow to take young siblings to school :-(

I just got off the phone with Nic-hole...I feel soooooo much better. Just to hear someone's voice that I know and talk and be happy! Oh happy happy joy joy! I have also started taking happy pills...But I don't think those have kicked in yet...I think I'm just happy! And no school for 4 weeks...Life might be good for awhile.

Boring days...Going through the motions...Ah well. Aunt and cousin from Virginia came down this weekend...Was ok. I now keep in touch with my cousin...Dunno what that's gonna be like.
I signed up for the YMCA today...The thing is 10x the size of the one in Plant City or Brandon. Hopefully I can start playing basketball again and maybe lift some weights...I ate a LOT today. Gonna go eat some more before I go to sleep...Maybe I'll gain some weight...What an idea!
I've also been thinking about some stuff lately that might inspire a poem some time in the near future! oOoOoOoOo...

I leave in the morning for South Carolina to stay with my aunt and uncle...Then Monday morning I'm off to Never Never Land...Err...I mean, Florida! WOooohhoooo! Gonna be a 5 day paradise...Much needed.

Well it's Christmas Eve I guess...Technically, anyways. I'm still sick as ever. Went through 3 boxes of tissues today and a gallon of gatorade. People should stop getting sick and we'll save millions of trees! Such a simple solution! Yea...Mad cow disease found in Washington state...Amazing.

Ok, got that stuff squared away...It looks somewhat presentable...In the process, I sneezed very violently and managed to get a major crick in my neck. Maybe if I sneeze again even harder it'll un-crick it...Or maybe I'll get another crick on the other side...Or maybe it'll just hurt really bad...Maybe...

Life is wonderful.
Yay, I got this thing free and it's working...It looks so...Plain...And I feel like shit...Gonna have to work on this some time soon
